# ONLINE MEDIC Architecture Skill

## When to activate
- User asks about "ONLINE MEDIC", "オンライン診療", "online consultation flow"
- Questions about Google Forms/Calendar/Meets integration with LINE Bot
- Implementing automated reminder/notification systems
- Booking code or tracking code system design
- Email to user ID mapping patterns
- Cron-based background job architecture

## What this skill provides
- Complete patient journey flow from friend add to video consultation
- Database schema (6 models) with relationships
- Booking code system (CL-XXXXX) for cross-platform mapping
- Email ↔ LINE ID mapping for Calendar attendee lookup
- Cron job patterns (every 5 minutes) for form sync and reminders
- Reminder deduplication strategy
- Video call options (Google Meets vs LIFF)
- Simplified architecture compared to ChatClinic (17 models → 6 models)

## Key concepts
- Booking codes bridge LINE and Google ecosystems
- Email mapping is critical for Calendar → LINE notifications
- Cron frequency balances timeliness with API rate limits
- Reminder deduplication prevents spam
- Separation: ChatClinic (hospital search/GPT) vs ONLINEMEDIC (consultations only)
